{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"id0e37770b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"7427"},"text":"§ 7427.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Student eligibility forms","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e37770c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Secretary shall require that, as part of an application for a grant under this subpart, each applicant shall maintain a file, with respect to each Indian child for whom the local educational agency provides a free public education, that contains a form that sets forth information establishing the status of the child as an Indian child eligible for assistance under this subpart, and that otherwise meets the requirements of subsection (b). All individual data collected shall be protected by the local educational agencies and only aggregated data shall be reported to the Secretary.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e37770d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Forms","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The form described in subsection (a) shall include—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37770e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" either—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37770f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id0e377710-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1/A/i"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"i"},"text":"(i)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the name of the tribe or band of Indians (as defined in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7491"},"text":"section 7491 of this title","children":[],"tail":") with respect to which the child claims membership;"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id0e377711-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1/A/ii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"ii"},"text":"(ii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the enrollment number establishing the membership of the child (if readily available); and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"clause","attrib":{"id":"id0e377712-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1/A/iii"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"iii"},"text":"(iii)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the name and address of the organization that maintains updated and accurate membership data for such tribe or band of Indians; or","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377713-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the name, the enrollment number (if readily available), and the name and address of the organization responsible for maintaining updated and accurate membership data, of any parent or grandparent of the child from whom the child claims eligibility under this subpart, if the child is not a member of the tribe or band of Indians (as so defined);","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377714-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a statement of whether the tribe or band of Indians (as so defined), with respect to which the child, or parent or grandparent of the child, claims membership, is federally recognized;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377715-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" the name and address of the parent or legal guardian of the child;","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377716-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a signature of the parent or legal guardian of the child that verifies the accuracy of the information supplied; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377717-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/b/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" any other information that the Secretary considers necessary to provide an accurate program profile.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e377718-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Statutory construction","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Nothing in this section shall be construed to affect a definition contained in ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7491"},"text":"section 7491 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e377719-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Documentation and types of proof","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Types of proof","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of determining whether a child is eligible to be counted for the purpose of computing the amount of a grant award under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7423"},"text":"section 7423 of this title","children":[],"tail":", the membership of the child, or any parent or grandparent of the child, in a tribe or band of Indians (as so defined) may be established by proof other than an enrollment number, notwithstanding the availability of an enrollment number for a member of such tribe or band. Nothing in subsection (b) shall be construed to require the furnishing of an enrollment number."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" No new or duplicative determinations","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Once a child is determined to be an Indian eligible to be counted for such grant award, the local educational agency shall maintain a record of such determination and shall not require a new or duplicate determination to be made for such child for a subsequent application for a grant under this subpart.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Previously filed forms","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"An Indian student eligibility form that was on file as required by this section on the day before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"December 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", and that met the requirements of this section, as this section was in effect on the day before "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"December 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", shall remain valid for such Indian student."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"e"},"text":"(e)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Monitoring and evaluation review","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" In general","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37771f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Review","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"For each fiscal year, in order to provide such information as is necessary to carry out the responsibility of the Secretary to provide technical assistance under this subpart, the Secretary shall conduct a monitoring and evaluation review of a sampling of the recipients of grants under this subpart. The sampling conducted under this subparagraph shall take into account the size of and the geographic location of each local educational agency.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377720-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Exception","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A local educational agency may not be held liable to the United States or be subject to any penalty, by reason of the findings of an audit that relates to the date of completion, or the date of submission, of any forms used to establish, before ","children":[{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-04-28"},"text":"April 28, 1988","children":[],"tail":", the eligibility of a child for an entitlement under the Indian Elementary and Secondary School Assistance Act."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377721-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" False information","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Any local educational agency that provides false information in an application for a grant under this subpart shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377722-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" be ineligible to apply for any other grant under this subpart; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377723-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" be liable to the United States for any funds from the grant that have not been expended.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377724-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/e/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Excluded children","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A student who provides false information for the form required under subsection (a) shall not be counted for the purpose of computing the amount of a grant under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7423"},"text":"section 7423 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e377725-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/f"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"f"},"text":"(f)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Tribal grant and contract schools","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"Notwithstanding any other provision of this section, in calculating the amount of a grant under this subpart to a tribal school that receives a grant or contract from the Bureau of Indian Education, the Secretary shall use only one of the following, as selected by the school:","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377726-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/f/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A count of the number of students in the schools certified by the Bureau.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377727-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/f/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A count of the number of students for whom the school has eligibility forms that comply with this section.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"id0e377728-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/g"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"g"},"text":"(g)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Timing of child counts","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"For purposes of determining the number of children to be counted in calculating the amount of a local educational agency’s grant under this subpart (other than in the case described in subsection (f)(1)), the local educational agency shall—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e377729-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/g/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" establish a date on, or a period not longer than 31 consecutive days during, which the agency counts those children, if that date or period occurs before the deadline established by the Secretary for submitting an application under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7424"},"text":"section 7424 of this title","children":[],"tail":"; and"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"id0e37772a-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795","identifier":"/us/usc/t20/s7427/g/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" determine that each such child was enrolled, and receiving a free public education, in a school of the agency on that date or during that period, as the case may be.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"id0e37772b-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10/tVI/s6117"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10, title VI, § 6117","children":[],"tail":", formerly title VII, § 7117, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110/tVII/s701"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110, title VII, § 701","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-01-08"},"text":"Jan. 8, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/115/1916"},"text":"115 Stat. 1916","children":[],"tail":"; renumbered title VI, § 6117, and amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/tVI"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, title VI","children":[],"tail":", §§ 6001(a), (b)(1), (7), 6002(i), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-10"},"text":"Dec. 10, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/2046"},"text":"129 Stat. 2046","children":[],"tail":", 2047, 2053.)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"id0e37772c-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"id0e37772d-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"id0e37772e-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Indian Elementary and Secondary School Assistance Act, referred to in subsec. (e)(1)(B), is title III of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1950-09-30/ch1124"},"text":"act Sept. 30, 1950, ch. 1124","children":[],"tail":", as added by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/92/318/tIV/s411/a"},"text":"Pub. L. 92–318, title IV, § 411(a)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1972-06-23"},"text":"June 23, 1972","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/86/335"},"text":"86 Stat. 335","children":[],"tail":", which was classified generally to subchapter III (§ 241aa et seq.) of chapter 13 of this title, prior to repeal by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/100/297/tV/s5352/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 100–297, title V, § 5352(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1988-04-28"},"text":"Apr. 28, 1988","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/102/414"},"text":"102 Stat. 414","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"priorProvisions","id":"id0e37772f-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Prior Provisions","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"A prior section 7427, ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/89/10/tVII/s7117"},"text":"Pub. L. 89–10, title VII, § 7117","children":[],"tail":", as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/103/382/tI/s101"},"text":"Pub. L. 103–382, title I, § 101","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1994-10-20"},"text":"Oct. 20, 1994","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/108/3727"},"text":"108 Stat. 3727","children":[],"tail":", related to intensified instruction for limited English proficient students, prior to the general amendment of former subchapter VII of this chapter by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/110"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–110","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"id0e377730-3a70-11f1-a648-bee82ed8a795"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6002(i)(1)","children":[],"tail":", inserted at end “All individual data collected shall be protected by the local educational agencies and only aggregated data shall be reported to the Secretary.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b)(1)(A)(i). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6001/b/7/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6001(b)(7)(A)","children":[],"tail":", made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7491"},"text":"section 7491 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6001/b/7/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6001(b)(7)(B)","children":[],"tail":", made technical amendment to reference in original act which appears in text as reference to "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7491"},"text":"section 7491 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/4"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6002(i)(4)","children":[],"tail":", added subsec. (d) and struck out former subsec. (d). Prior to amendment, text read as follows: “For purposes of determining whether a child is eligible to be counted for the purpose of computing the amount of a grant award under "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t20/s7423"},"text":"section 7423 of this title","children":[],"tail":", the membership of the child, or any parent or grandparent of the child, in a tribe or band of Indians (as so defined) may be established by proof other than an enrollment number, notwithstanding the availability of an enrollment number for a member of such tribe or band. Nothing in subsection (b) of this section shall be construed to require the furnishing of an enrollment number.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6002(i)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), redesignated subsec. (e) as (d) and struck out former subsec. (d) which related to forms and standards of proof."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (e). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6002(i)(3)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated subsec. (f) as (e). Former subsec. (e) redesignated (d)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (f). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/5"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–95, § 6002(i)(5)","children":[],"tail":", which directed substitution of “Bureau of Indian Education” for “Bureau of Indian Affairs” in subsec. (f) as redesignated by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/95/s6002/i/4"},"text":"section 6002(i)(4) of Pub. L. 114–95","